items.headline: Learn strategies to build your personal and professional network.
objectives_summary: At the end of this course, you will be able to apply a series of strategies to manage and build your personal and professional networks to help you create a stress buffer or support in challenging times. We’ll ask you to assess your connections, create a network map and develop a plan to maximise your relationships. Along the way we’ll also give you a lot of practical tips for creating strong, healthy networks that support you in times of stress.
